Regulation (EC) No 2007/2000 is hereby amended as follows:
1. Article 1 shall be replaced by the following:
2. in Article 4, paragraph 4 shall be replaced by the following:
(a) 12 000 tonnes (net weight) for sugar products originating in Bosnia and Herzegovina;
(b) 180 000 tonnes (net weight) for sugar products originating in Montenegro and the customs territories of Serbia or Kosovo.’;
3. Annex I shall be replaced by the text appearing in the Annex to this Regulation.
